  "detailed_description": "<strong>Skellies Ain't Scary</strong> is a <strong>bullet hell rogue-like</strong> with minimalist graphics. Delve into deep dungeons and collect a plethora of guns and items. Build the strongest synergies and beat all the bosses. Pests and foes lie deep within, eager to stop you in your tracks as you venture past floor after floor of increasingly mortal challenges. Uncover the secrets of the dungeon and collect the lost treasures that await you.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/06fc4c0c5bce45f811ce0b9338caef36.poster.avif?t=1681516818\" width=642 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/06fc4c0c5bce45f811ce0b9338caef36.webm?t=1681516818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/06fc4c0c5bce45f811ce0b9338caef36.mp4?t=1681516818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>FAST PACED GAMEPLAY</i></strong></h2><strong>Unlimited ammo</strong> and <strong>one second reloads</strong> beg you to sweep the dungeons at lightning speeds. Enemies swarm you in droves, while you bob and weave manically to avoid their chaotic sprays of bullets.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/1431471cee4136ac4aab0135c5bc2d0c.poster.avif?t=1681516818\" width=642 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/1431471cee4136ac4aab0135c5bc2d0c.webm?t=1681516818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/1431471cee4136ac4aab0135c5bc2d0c.mp4?t=1681516818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>WEAPON AND ITEM VARIETY</i></strong></h2>The dungeon floors boast a remarkable amount of <strong>unique items</strong> with special abilities and <strong>varied gun play</strong>. Double item slots allow for fun, game breaking combos, and with a range of <strong>50+ items</strong> and <strong>25+ guns</strong>, the possibilities are far and wide.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/94cfc053fb8140a54629b7e701e3a5f0.poster.avif?t=1681516818\" width=642 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/94cfc053fb8140a54629b7e701e3a5f0.webm?t=1681516818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956930/extras/94cfc053fb8140a54629b7e701e3a5f0.mp4?t=1681516818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>HUB WORLD</i></strong></h2>A spacious hub world containing <strong>trophies of your achievements</strong> and <strong>unlockable equipment</strong> that can affect future runs.",
